    "description": "MarkLines Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, operates an automotive industry portal in Japan, China, the rest of Asia, North America, Europe, and internationally. The company's information platform offers online information services, including sales, production, and model changes, technologies, vehicle teardown data and analyses, component supplier information, and other proprietary information in Japanese, English, and Chinese. It also provides B2B promotion and advertisement services that include product information, promotional emails, and banner ads under the LINES name to its information platform members. In addition, the company engages in consulting, vehicle disassembly and measurement, personnel placement, market forecast information sales, vehicle and parts procurement agency, and disassembly survey activities. It serves component supplier sales and marketing departments, as well as vehicle OEM development and purchasing departments of companies. MarkLines Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
